            "id": "4574358",
            "title": "Perella Weinberg to expand in UK with Gleacher Shacklock acquisition",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">Perella Weinberg Partners (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PWP\" title=\"Perella Weinberg Partners\">PWP</a></span></span>) is set to acquire the London-headquartered independent advisory firm Gleacher Shacklock.</p>\n<p>Terms of the acquisition were not disclosed.</p>\n<p><span>The transaction is expected to close in the second half.</span></p>\n<p><span>The acquisition is expected to expand Perella Weinberg's presence in the UK market. The country is said to be the largest advisory market in Europe, and cross-border transaction volume between the UK, Europe, and North America continues to accelerate.</span></p>\n<p><span>Shares were 1.57% higher at $20.75 during Monday pre-market trading.</span></p>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
